## Command Line Tools

```bash
# PDF text extraction
pdftotext input.pdf output.txt

# Merge PDFs
qpdf --empty --pages file1.pdf file2.pdf -- merged.pdf

# DOCX to markdown
pandoc document.docx -o output.md
```

